dxf2svg.sally
Class Symbol

java.lang.Object
  dxf2svg.sally.Symbol
Direct Known Subclasses:
Symbol.ByteSymbol, Symbol.DoubleSymbol, Symbol.IntegerSymbol, Symbol.ObjectSymbol, Symbol.StringSymbol, Symbol.UnorderedStringList
public class Symbol
extends java.lang.Object

This class encapsulates a symbol (read variable) in the SALly language. It can hold one of the following forms of primative data types:

  • integer - 4 bytes
  • byte - 1 byte
  • double - floating point number.
  • String - Java String object.

Symbol uses a factory method to create these objects so it is easily expanded to include a wider range and/or more complex data types.

Version:
0.01 - May 20, 2003
Author:
Andrew Nisbet
